profile:
We are a home renovation, remodel, and handyman services company. 

With over a decade of experience, we offer quality workmanship and attention to detail that fits any budget. We pride ourselves on attention to detail and customization of work for each project we undertake. Whether your project is indoors, outdoors, a small fix or a large-scale renovation, we are able to meet your need. 

BATHROOMS
Whether you are looking for luxury finishes or something simple and functional, we've got you covered. 

FLOORING
Vinyl and laminate floors are on the rise, as they are durable, versatile, and come in a variety of attractive colours, shades and textures. We also install hardwood floors and tiles.

DECKS
Have us build you a new deck or simply refurbish your existing deck.

OUTDOOR WORK
Let us revitalize your outdoor space! Whether its a new shed, a rock garden, pavers, stone features, or mulch and sod installation, we've got you covered. 

STORAGE SOLUTIONS
We'll help you create more storage space so you can better utilize your cold room/cantina, basement, garage, and shed. We can also convert your extra bedroom into a large walk-in closet. 

GENERAL HANDYMAN REPAIRS & MAINTENANCE
Drywall repairs, painting, staining, electrical fixture replacements, trim carpentry installations, and other home repair needs.

profile:
Handy Sammy is a small family based business that specializes in small, medium-sized and larger home repairs and improvements. We are a father and son team that has over 50 years of combined experience in home renovation, new construction, and property maintenance. We also have been recognised for our creativity and forward thinking in many elements of design and often asked to be hired as a consultation service for such things as basement or addition layouts, structured wiring, and audio video distribution. From fixing a leaky faucet to remodelling a bathroom, you can trust the experienced Handy Sammy to repair, remodel or renovate your home. Maybe it’s just that “honey do list” that gets longer and longer that you need some help with. Whatever your project is, we'll make sure it's done right the first time. 

Handy Sammy is highly skilled craftsmen. We are bonded and insured, so you know he will get the job done right the first time. Handy Sammy will arrive on time in clean, in a vehicle that’s stocked with all the tools and parts to get most jobs done quickly and efficiently. We offer Home Repair Service You Can Trust!

Handy Sammy takes the worry and frustration out of home improvement, repairs and remodelling. After your work is completed, and you are fully satisfied do we talk about payment. Our goal is to provide customer service that exceeds your expectations Satisfaction Guaranteed
